OL,3,CPolice officer dismissed over
OL,4,Coffensive messages
OL,6,FA police officer in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fhas been sacked after sending "highly
OL,8,Finappropriate and offensive" messages
OL,9,Fvia WhatsApp.
OL,11,FThe office of the Police Ombudsman
OL,12,Fsaid the messages, which were sent
OL,13,Fwhile the officer was on duty,
OL,14,Fcontained material which was
OL,15,Fsectarian, racist, homophobic, anti-
OL,16,Fsemitic, misogynistic and sexualised.
