OL,6,FThe complainant contacted the Police
OL,7,FOmbudsman when the Police Service of
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland (PSNI) officer
OL,9,Fcontinued to send the material,
OL,10,Fdespite being asked to stop on two
OL,11,Foccasions.
OL,13,FNikki Davis, director of
OL,14,Finvestigations at the ombudsman's
OL,15,Foffice, said: "Digital analysis of the
OL,16,Fpolice officer's phone showed that he
OL,17,Fhad sent multiple images and videos,
OL,18,Fwhich were highly inappropriate and
OL,19,Foffensive, to the complainant, other
OL,20,Fmembers of the public and other police
OL,21,Fofficers
OL,26,@wD@OOU
