OL,6,F"This was not a one-off, isolated
OL,7,Fincident, which could potentially be
OL,8,Fattributed to a lapse in judgment.
OL,10,F"It was sustained, consistent
OL,11,Fbehaviour, exacerbated by the police
OL,12,Fofficer's view, when interviewed by
OL,13,Four investigators, that he did not
OL,14,Fconsider the material to be offensive
OL,15,For his actions to be in breach of the
OL,16,FPSNI Code of Ethics."
