OL,6,FMrs Davis added: "When this kind of
OL,7,Fmessaging specifically targets women
OL,8,Fand combines sexual, racist and
OL,9,Fsectarian references, it moves into
OL,10,Fthe realm of online gender-based hate
OL,11,Fspeech
OL,13,F"For a police officer to display these
OL,14,Fattitudes and behaviours towards women
OL,15,Fis unacceptable, and specifically
OL,16,Fundermines the PSNI's commitment to
OL,17,Fending violence against women and
OL,18,Fgirls.
