OL,6,FThe PPS directed no prosecution.
OL,8,FA misconduct file was then submitted
OL,9,Fto the PSNI Professional Standards
OL,10,FDepartment.
OL,12,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher held a
OL,13,Fspecial hearing, after which the
OL,14,Fpolice officer was dismissed.
OL,16,FHe was found to have breached a number
OL,17,Fof articles of the PSNI Code of
OL,18,FEthics, including those relating to
OL,19,Fprofessional duty, equality and
OL,20,Fintegrity.
