OL,6,FEight police officers, who received
OL,7,Fthe messages and failed to report or
OL,8,Fchallenge them, were referred to the
OL,9,FPSNI in relation to potential breaches
OL,10,Fof the code of ethics.
OL,12,FThe Police Ombudsman received the
OL,13,Fcomplaint about the police officer in
OL,14,FJuly 2023.
