OL,6,FThe office has previously called for
OL,7,Ffast-tracking powers in cases where it
OL,8,Fis clear from an early stage in an
OL,9,Finvestigation that there is
OL,10,Fcriminality or gross misconduct which
OL,11,Fcould result in an officer being
OL,12,Fdismissed without undue delay.
OL,14,FThe chairman of the Police Federation
OL,15,Ffor Northern Ireland, Liam Kelly, said
OL,16,Fsuch behaviour would not be tolerated.
OL,18,FHe said: "Police officers are held to
OL,19,Fthe highest possible standards both on
OL,20,Fand off duty.
